      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">12.101</ph> Policy.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d704e8" class="- topic/p ">The head of the agency shall—</p>
         <ol id="d677e16" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d704e12" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> Conduct
market research to determine whether <ph rev="FAC 2022-01 December 6, 2021" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-018?>commercial products, commercial
services,<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 12.101 by removing the term “commercial items” wherever it appears and adding “commercial products, commercial services,” in its place.?></ph> or nondevelopmental items are available that could
meet the agency’s requirements;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d704e22" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> Acquire <ph rev="FAC 2022-01 December 6, 2021" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-018?>commercial products, commercial
services,<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 12.101 by removing the term “commercial items” wherever it appears and adding “commercial products, commercial services,” in its place.?></ph> or nondevelopmental items when they are available
to meet the needs of the agency; and</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d704e32" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph> Require
prime contractors and subcontractors at all tiers to incorporate,
to the maximum extent practicable, <ph rev="FAC 2022-01 December 6, 2021" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-018?>commercial products, commercial
services,<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 12.101 by removing the term “commercial items” wherever it appears and adding “commercial products, commercial services,” in its place.?></ph> or nondevelopmental items as components of items
supplied to the agency.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
